text: Alicia Vikander (born October 3, 1988) is a Swedish actress. She will play Alice Deane in Seventh Son. She has also been in lots of other movies, such as the 2015 Ex Machina. Vikander was born in Gothenburg, Sweden. ==References== Category:Swedish movie actors Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:Actors from Gothenburg
